Package: PBMExperiment
Title: Tools for the analysis of Protein Binding Microarrays
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: person("Patrick", "Kimes", email = "patrick.kimes@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Classes and methods for the organization and analysis of transcription factor binding affinities
  quantified in vitro using Protein Binding Microarrays.
